seurat_known_markers.Rd

Seurat known markers example

data(seurat_known_markers)

Format

An object of class KnownMarkers with 16 rows and 10 columns.

Value

KnownMarkers.

Note

Updated 2020-01-30.

Examples

data(seurat_known_markers)
